metadata.name: TGOA-064 " REINA.ONI.MODE "
metadata.description:
THE GIRLS OR ARMAMENT - NFT BATTLE ROYALE - SEASON_3

1.You can bid the girl off at auction.And you can use her as your own SENSHI.

2.The top3 girls and their owners are awarded the following three characters as NFTs.

- 1st girl -  TGOA-S01 " KINRYU "
-2nd girl - TGOA-S02 " GINRYU "
-3rd girl - TGOA-036 " MARIKA. SAKAI "
